Description:
Soaring Spaces, Stunning Renovation, Sought After Location
A quiet cul-de-sac is out front, poolside entertaining waits behind, a quality renovation lies within and great family value starts right here!
Designed around a grand garden atrium with architectural elements as a backdrop to state-of-the-art interiors, this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home makes the most of its northerly aspect with walls of glass and soaring cathedral ceilings for the expansive lounge and dining domain, whilst a long entrance hall zones the master privately away from the secondary bedrooms.
A showcase of cutting edge detail with thick stone benchtops, herringbone splashbacks and engineered Oak flooring, this elite family home stars a Smeg 6 burner oven and butlers pantry in the gourmet kitchen, designer bathrooms with full height tiling (one a frameless screened ensuite, the other with freestanding bath) and modern comforts of ducted heating and cooling.
Set in 753sqm approx, grounds with a deep solar heated pool beyond elevated al fresco entertaining, a double auto garage and a poolside bungalow with ensuite, walk-in robes and split system air-con (perfect for teenage independence or guest accommodation), this mid-century marvel even has a premier McKinnon Secondary College Zone location close to the 64 tram, a selection of great schools and sports grounds, North Rd shops, station and bus route plus major road access for an easy bayside commute.

Description:
Period-Style, As-New Prestige & a Zone Position!
Find family accommodation with period inspiration in the ultimate McKinnon College Zone location! Secluded to the rear within one block of Ormond's station and shops, this as-new four bedroom, three bathroom, dual zone home takes inspiration from its period neighbours with a high-gabled terracotta-roofed design graced with lovely leadlight, rich hardwood floors and classic joinery.
Designed to adapt to modern family life with a gracious formal lounge, spacious family zone and a vast master-suite, there's a flexible ground-floor bedroom beside a full bathroom (perfect as ground-floor master or extra-large home-office) and a powered landing area to use as a study nook! Appointed in contemporary prestige style with a state-of-the-art Smeg appliance kitchen and glossy floor-to-ceiling tiled bathrooms (including an ensuite), this climate-controlled home features thick stone benchtops (even for the large laundry), pretty plantation-shutters and great storage with built-in and walk-in-robes.
Set in carefree lawn-free surrounds with a bluestone paved courtyard wrapping around at the rear and a generous double auto-garage on wide exposed aggregate-paved turning-circle out front, this is the ideal combination of timeless living and the carefree life. Even this lifetime location combines family life and an easy lifestyle; just off the Ormond retail and restaurant strip, within 200m of the stations and an easy walk to McKinnon Secondary College!

Description:
Exceptional contemporary living with indoor-outdoor lifestyle
Situated in the heart of Ormond and only a 500-metre walk to Ormond Station, this ground floor contemporary apartment is perfect for first home buyers, investors or downsizers.
This apartment offers a naturally lit open plan living, with a wrap-around courtyard and a seamless flow of indoor-outdoor lifestyle for effortless entertaining all year round.
Comprising of 2 bedrooms with built in robes, ensuite and second bathroom, European style laundry and a fully functional kitchen with a 1.8m waterfall island bench, microwave recess and SMEG dishwasher and appliances.
Continuing the open plan living, this apartment has floor to ceiling doors with access to the landscaped courtyard from every room. Further amenities include: high ceilings, corridor entrance, dark oak floors, linen closet, block-out blinds, plantation shutters, video intercom entry, split system in open living, wall mounted heaters in each bedroom, merbau deck, storage cage and a secure basement car space with an electric gate.
Perfectly located close to Ormond Station, North Road shops, Duncan McKinnon reserve, public and private schools, Monash University (Caulfield) and only a short distance from Chadstone Shopping Centre, GESAC and Brighton Beach.

Description:
Zone Deco with land To grow.
Open a time-capsule of Art Deco beauty and create a new era of gracious living in the McKinnon College Zone. A classic Art Deco example from the grand proportions of bay-windowed living, to a curvaceous eat-in kitchen, to the terrazzo-floored bathroom, this substantial solid-brick home is ready to step out of the past and into the future.
See the beauty in exquisite detail (including a distinctive curved and tiled fireplace, elegant etched glass and lofty deep-corniced ceilings) and work with an easily extended two bedroom floorplan featuring ducted heating, an air-conditioner and French doors to deep potential-filled approx 720sq.m gardens.
Highlight the divine Deco detail, extend past the existing brick garage and make the most of an increasingly rare Zone original. Alternatively, see the potential to redevelop (subject to Council Approval) and reap the rewards of the Zone address with the bus to the bay, Ormond station and Monash University at the door.
For more information please contact Nick Blow 0411 831 731 from Barry Plant today.

Description:
Sunny Spaces only Steps to the Village
Peacefully placed in a smartly rendered block, this sunlit apartment is a real find for first-home buyers and investors. Boasting an elevated front position, the freshly-presented home has a floorplan that really stands out from the others thanks to true appeal and liveability. And the location just adds more to the fabulous lifestyle on offer - boasting easy access to North Road for buses and stress-free commuting, this locality also enjoys supreme proximity to Ormonds station, eateries and shops.
Flushed with natural light, the hub of the home is the spacious combined living/dining zone that flanks a beech-toned and sleek black kitchen multiple windows take in pretty leafy views, whilst the front-facing balcony is the perfect place to soak up morning sunshine. The two beautiful bedrooms can both accommodate a double bed with ease, they feature mirrored robes and lovely north-facing windows a sparkling white bathroom with handy laundry taps services the home, while wrapping up the package are a split system, ample storage, intercom entry & auto-gated carport parking.

Description:
Stylish seclusion with exacting attention to detail
Finished with quality and class, this private 2 bedroom single level town residence has a love of easy entertaining. Enjoying the warmth of polished boards throughout and customised cabinetry, this beautiful home enjoys a stylish main bedroom (fitted BIRs) with stunning semi ensuite with double spa, 2nd double bedroom (fitted BIRs) with French doors to a private courtyard, fitted laundry and powder room (2nd toilet) and a vast open plan entertaining area with study niche (stone desktop) and a fabulous granite kitchen with Smeg stainless steel appliances, integrated Bosch dishwasher & breakfast bar, the stainless steel French door fridge will also be included. Bi-fold doors lead to the covered deck in lush leafy gardens. More than you'd expect, this contemporary haven features R/C ducted air conditioning, granite benchtops, custom made Holland blinds throughout, the main bedroom has custom made drapes and blinds, ample storage, solar hot water and internal access to an auto garage with rear rollerdoor for extra parking. Presented like new in the sought after McKinnon Secondary College zone, footsteps to McKinnon Primary School, Monash Uni bus and the gorgeous Joyce Park, moments to North Road shops and train, McKinnon Reserve and a great selection of shopping centres

Description:
Low-Maintenance Family Oasis
This Quality low-maintenance oasis takes easy family living to a new level! This substantial two-storey floorplan offers three bedrooms, study area, two bathrooms and dual living zones.
A carefree family lifestyle with a well-zoned floorplan featuring an in-demand ground-floor master, a dedicated first-floor kids level and living upstairs and down. Oriented to maximise north sun with defined areas to lounge and dine facing north to the courtyard and a large first-floor lounge with the same sunny aspect, theres even more room to live outdoors with a covered al fresco area with BBQ gas-point.
Quality-appointed with European appliances including a Bosch dishwasher for the kitchen, a stylish stone-finished two-way ensuite for the master and a mix of plush carpets and Grand Oak timber flooring, the home has climate controlling reverse-cycle air-conditioning (on each level), ducted heating (throughout), ceiling fans (for almost room) and a large external blind (for the sun-catching upstairs window).
With generous storage (including understair and mirror robes) and quality window-furnishings (including master block-outs), the home is secured by Crimsafe security doors with the added peace-of-mind of an auto-garage plus a sheltered carspace. With Ormonds quiet new station and shopping strip within minutes walk, Glen Huntly Primary School and the private schools within dash and the bus to both Monash University campuses close, this is a new level of easy family living to suit every stage of family life. For more information about this carefree family home contact Claude Mery at Buxton Bentleigh on 0422 455 848 or the Buxton Office on 9563 9933. ALL ENQUIRIES MUST INCLUDE A CONTACT NUMBER.

Description:
Classic Charm, Modern Convenience
Indulge in a lifestyle of classic charm and modern convenience with this solid brick Art Deco delight inside the coveted McKinnon Secondary College zone.
Enjoying the benefits of no common land, its own driveway and street frontage, a secure and private front yard that's perfect for kids and the family pet, the positive appeal also extends into the bright single-level interior of this timeless beauty.
High ceilings and loads of natural light grace every corner of the home, while a gas heater provides plenty of warmth to the large and inviting lounge.
Cooks of any level will appreciate the spacious nature of the large kitchen that forms part of the casual open-plan living area, while a bright main bathroom comfortably services three generous-sized bedrooms.
Furthermore, this first-class investment, smart downsizing option or home for the professional couple or young family also features two toilets, a single lock-up garage and a premier lifestyle location that's within walking distance of Ormond train station, bus services, popular parks and Ormond Road shops and cafes and moments away from prestigious schools and the foreshore.

Secure and Spacious
A fabulous opportunity with sleek finishes and fittings, and stylish presentation all delivered in a secure, private, contemporary, ground-floor apartment. You'll love the relaxing lifestyle, the space to entertain indoors or outside, the light bright interior and the neutral decor. The entrance hall leads past the 2 double-size bedrooms (with mirror-fronted built-in wardrobes and their own private balconies) to a sunlight-flooded open living room with stone and stainless steel kitchen. Description:
Modern Grace with Family Space in the Zone
Offering a modern take on Ormonds historic hill precinct, this beautiful 3 bedroom 2-bathroom solid brick residence combines a spacious family friendly floorplan with a low maintenance outdoors and a premier McKinnon Secondary School Zone location.
Warm and welcoming with an open plan living area boasting a plush-pile lounge room and a polished timber-floored dining zone, this outstanding home flows effortlessly to a modern neutral kitchen with a Chef oven cooktop, tiled splashback and breakfast bar, offering convenience and a perfect window view of the backyard.
On the other side of the home is a private wing of well-proportioned bedrooms. The front-of-house master bedroom with a large walk-in wardrobe and a skylit ensuite is followed by two side-by-side bedrooms which share the second skylit bathroom featuring both shower and bath facilities and a stand-alone toilet.
Outdoor activities also come naturally as you push away the double sliding doors and enter the backyard complete with a timber deck, sail-shaded courtyard and lawned area. And dont forget the ducted heating, split-system air-con, a separate laundry and double garage.
In a coveted location, its walking distance to Ormond Primary School, McKinnon & Ormond Stations and North Road buses with Allnut Park, Wattle Reserve & the Centre Road shopping strip all close by.

Description:
Period Charm, Modern Upgrade, Prime Zone Position
Appreciate the beauty of the past, enjoy the quality of today and capitalise on a location to last a lifetime.
Graced with a contemporary upgrade against a beautifully detailed backdrop of high ornate ceilings, cast iron fireplaces plus a mix of Baltic Pine and Victorian Ash floors, this stunning period home zones three bedrooms at the front beside an elegant entrance hall, expansive living and dining beyond a quality kitchen with breakfast bar and great al fresco entertaining in lush lawned and established gardens.
With full height tiling in the luxe designer bathroom, heating and split system air-con for comfort, alarm for security, a pull down ladder to a spacious storage loft (2.5m X 5.5m) and a car space to park, this home has all the space youd want to build your nest and in a prime McKinnon Secondary College Zone location should you choose to invest.
Best of all, it has everything youll need in close proximity including Joyce park, Centre Rds vibrant shopping strip, McKinnon Reserve and Secondary College and a fast commute to Chadstone or Southlands train station and retail therapy.
ALL ENQUIRIES MUST INCLUDE A CONTACT NUMBER.

Description:
Hideaway on Holloway with 2 car spaces
Escape the rat race at the end of each day and retreat to the peace and calm of this inviting two bedroom apartment. Situated on the top floor of a neatly maintained group it truly is a tranquil hideaway, well removed from the world outside. Despite its quiet locale, it enjoys an ultra convenient position just moments to the station, shops, bus stops and parks this really is the best of both worlds!
On offer is a spacious and sun filled abode with lounge (split system heating/cooling), private balcony and well equipped eat in kitchen with stainless steel appliances. A bright bathroom/laundry and separate WC service the two bedrooms, both of which feature built in storage. Secure intercom entry ensures peace of mind whilst undercover parking is an added bonus. Walk to Ormond village and station, grab a coffee at one of the many fabulous cafes it is all here and ready to be enjoyed!
